data.description: Welcome to your dream family home, where grandeur meets comfort in this magnificent 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence. Situated in a highly sought-after Kingston neighborhood, this spacious abode promises a lifestyle of elegance and convenience that will delight every member of your family. As you approach this stately home, you'll be captivated by its timeless curb appeal. The meticulously landscaped front yard sets the stage for what lies inside.  Upon entering the grand foyer, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light, high ceilings, and gleaming hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the main level. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the open-concept living area. Perfectly designed for hosting family gatherings or entertaining friends, the spacious living room featuring a cozy fireplace, makes it the ideal spot for cozy evenings in. Adjacent to the living room is a formal dining area, perfect for hosting elegant dinner parties. The eat in kitchen that features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinetry will delight the home chef.  The five generously-sized bedrooms provide the perfect retreat for every member of the family. The primary suite, located on the main floor, is a true sanctuary, boasting a spa-like ensuite bath with a luxurious soaking tub, dual vanities, and a separate shower! If that isn't enough...the bonus media room and loft space located on the second floor will definitely be a added treat!  Finally, step outside to your private outdoor haven. The expansive backyard offers endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation.      This remarkable 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence offers an unrivaled combination of luxury, comfort, and entertainment possibilities. If you're seeking a home where your family can thrive and create lasting memories, this is the one you've been waiting for.    Schedule your private viewing today and discover the lifestyle that awaits you in this exceptional family home!
